=== Films === * *{{ill|Nabbie’s Love|ja|ナビィの恋|qq=draft|qq=draft}}* (1999). * *{{ill|Akaokuro|ja|アコークロー|qq=draft|qq=draft}}* (2007). * *{{ill|Sadaka|ja|サーダカー|qq=draft|qq=draft}}* (2007). * *{{ill|The Tempest|ja|テンペスト (池上永一)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}* (2011). * *{{ill|It Comes (film)|ja|ぼぎわんが、来る|qq=draft|qq=draft}}* (2018).
=== Novels === * *{{ill|Bagaa Jimanu Panasu|ja|バガージマヌパナス|qq=draft|qq=draft}}* by Eichi Ikegami. * *{{ill|Yuta ga Aishita Tantei|ja|ユタが愛した探偵|qq=draft|qq=draft}}* by Yasuo Uchida. == See Also == * {{ill|Itako|ja|イタコ|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Utaki|ja|御嶽 (沖縄)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Noro|ja|ノロ|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Ryukyu Kingdom|ja|琉球王国|qq=draft|qq=draft}} * {{ill|Ryukyu Shinto|ja|琉球神道|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
